                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="characterBox">
                    <img class="characterImg" src="{{asset("bundles/app/image/haunted/diceschool/diceschool_001_character1.jpg")}}">
                    <div class="characterText">
                        <span class="bold size18">채미리</span><br>
                        <span>염라대왕에게 약속을 잘못하여 쫓기는 중인 채미리. 언제라도 문이 벌컥 열릴것 같다.</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td class="characterBox">
                    <img class="characterImg" src="{{asset("bundles/app/image/haunted/diceschool/diceschool_004_character1.jpg")}}">
                    <div class="characterText">
